ZH: 他正在厨房里洗盘子。
EN: He is washing the dishes in the kitchen.

ZH: 我们在大盘里放了很多食物。
EN: We put a lot of food on the big plate.

ZH: 盘子里的水已经干了。
EN: The water in the dish has dried up.

ZH: 这个小盘子很精致。
EN: This small dish is very delicate.

ZH: 他一口气把盘子里的所有食物都吃完了。
EN: He finished all the food in the plate in one go.

ZH: 这个菜盘是从中国带来的。
EN: This serving plate was brought from China.

ZH: 他掀开了银盖盘里的菜。
EN: He uncovered the food in the silver covered dish.

ZH: 这个中国盘是她的收藏。
EN: This Chinese plate is her collection.

ZH: 盘子里的蛋糕看起来很美味。
EN: The cake in the dish looks delicious.

ZH: 她将盘子里的食物分给了大家。
EN: She shared the food in the dish with everyone.

ZH: 他把盘子里的米饭都吃光了。
EN: He finished all the rice in the dish.

ZH: 这碗盘里装了很多水果。
EN: This bowl is filled with a lot of fruits.

ZH: 他用一块布擦干了盘子里的水。
EN: He used a cloth to wipe the water in the dish.

ZH: 盘子上有一只精致的花。
EN: There is a delicate flower on the plate.

ZH: 我们在盘子里装了一大碗羊肉汤。
EN: We served a big bowl of mutton soup in the dish.

ZH: 盘里的糕点看起来很美味。
EN: The pastries in the plate look delicious.

ZH: 他把盘子放在了架子上。
EN: He placed the dish on the shelf.

ZH: 盘子里的水果甜甜的。
EN: The fruits in the dish are sweet.

ZH: 婆婆用她的礼物盘盛放水果。
EN: Grandma used her gift plate to serve fruits.

ZH: 盘子里装满了五彩的小石头。
EN: The dish is filled with colorful pebbles.
